  <h1>Version 2.3</h1>
  <ul>
    <li class="addition">+ Massive improvements to the image editor. You can now resize the box with handles, scroll to zoom the image, and pan by clicking on the image.</li>
    <li class="addition">+ There is now an indicator to show which color you have selected in the editor.</li>
